 On Dec 6, 2011, at 6:29 AM, Matthias Felleisen wrote:
 
 >=20
 > Align windows vertically
 > Align windows horizontally=20
 
 I prefer
 
 Split Window Vertically
 Split Window Horizontally
 
 ... because after all, this menu entry is about subdivision of space =
 (the frame), not about the alignment of two independent entities. As =
 evidence I point out that when you change from one to the other, the =
 shape of the frame doesn't change.
 
 Substituting "Frame" for window would be shorter, but might be less (or =
 more?) easily understood.
 
 John
 
 
